body:
Marvel lanza el póster de Captain Marvel para Latinoamérica

Carol Danvers (Brie Larson) es la misteriosa persona que fue buscada por Nick Fury (Samuel L. Jackson) en la última escena de Avengers: Infinity War, y ella aparecerá en el todavía sin título Avengers 4, presumiblemente para ayudar a acabar con Thanos. Pero antes de eso, ella tiene su propia historia que contar.

Cuando la película llegue a los cines el 8 de marzo de 2019, será la vigésima primera…

summary: MCU characters as things I’ve said vol. 2 (trying to recreate the magic)
body:
MCU characters as things ive said during school.

Vol. 2:

MCU characters as things I’ve said vol. 2 (trying to recreate the magic)

Tony Stark: “This is bullshit. Homework is bullshit. My teacher is bullshit. My parents are bullshit.”

Drax: “The bus? Loud.”

Stephen Strange: “I just hate everyone here.”

Peter Parker: “Why did you leave the skeleton army in my locker?”

Nebula: “Math makes me want to die. Not because it’s math, I like math, I just FUCKING hate my math teacher.”

Nick Fury: “what in the goddamn fuck happened here? And why do I have to fix it?”

Carol: “I walked the mile. I’m not a pussy, I stand up to the man.”

Steve: “What are you talking about? I’m an angel child, bitch.”

Bucky: “THAT WAS NOT FUNNY IN THE SLIGHTEST. MY ARM OH MY GOD? STOP LAUGHING”

Thanos holding a full water bottle: “This bitch empty! YEET!” *lands in trash can*

Gamora: “that’s it. This is the end. I’m dying.”

Natasha: “I was the first one done with the test, suck My dick.”

Clint, flipping a water bottle on top of a book leaning against the wall: “DID YOU SEE THAT? I LANDED THAT SHIT DUDE.”

Rocket: “remember to Eat ass, smoke grass, sled fast fifth graders.”

Groot: “I am Groot, bitch.”

Sam: “if we fail, at least I know I did it for the meme.”

Mantis: “Was that sarcasm? I don’t get that.”

Pepper: “Jesus i need to organize my locker.”

Bruce: “I aced that science test and I literally just bullshitted it?”

T’Challa: “WOMEN ARE QUEENS”

Shuri: “IF SHE BREATHE, SHE A THOOOTTTT!”

Okyoe: “Where’s my fucking spear. I stg I’ll fight that whore.”

Quill: “I’m the fucking best what are you talking about I hate myself.”
